rna_counts = readRDS('rna_counts.RDS')
cell_label = readRDS('cell_type.RDS')

rna_object = CreateSeuratObject(counts = rna_counts,assay = 'RNA')
rna_object = NormalizeData(object = rna_object)
## Normalizing layer: counts
rna_object = FindVariableFeatures(rna_object,nfeatures = 3000)
## Finding variable features for layer counts
rna_object = ScaleData(rna_object)
## Centering and scaling data matrix
rna_object$cell_type = cell_label[colnames(rna_object),1]


#identifying top marker genes for each cell-type
Idents(rna_object) = 'cell_type'
marker_genes = c()
for (cell_class in unique(cell_label$cell_type)) {
  markers = FindMarkers(rna_object, ident.1 = cell_class, ident.2 = NULL, only.pos = TRUE)
  print(cell_class);print(rownames(markers)[1:10])
  marker_genes = c(marker_genes,rownames(markers)[1:10])
}

#Get the imputed values of all methods
annotations <- GetGRangesFromEnsDb(ensdb = EnsDb.Hsapiens.v86)
seqlevels(annotations) <- paste0('chr', seqlevels(annotations))
genome(annotations) <- "hg38"
atac_counts = readRDS('atac_counts.RDS')
atac = CreateChromatinAssay(counts = atac_counts,sep = c("-", "-"),annotation = annotations,
                                 fragments = 'pbmc_granulocyte_sorted_10k_atac_fragments.tsv.gz')
## Computing hash
atac = CreateSeuratObject(counts = atac,assay = 'ATAC')

Signac_imputation = GeneActivity(object = atac,features = marker_genes)
## Extracting gene coordinates
## Extracting reads overlapping genomic regions
Signac_imputation = t(Signac_imputation)


rownames(atac_counts) = chartr(old = '-',new = '_',x = rownames(atac_counts))
MAESTRO_imputation = MAESTRO::ATACCalculateGenescore(inputMat = atac_counts)
MAESTRO_imputation = MAESTRO_imputation[intersect(rownames(MAESTRO_imputation),marker_genes),]
MAESTRO_imputation = t(MAESTRO_imputation)

UnpairReg_imputation = readRDS('unpairreg_imputation.RDS')
supermap_imputation = readRDS('supermap_imputation.RDS')
measured = rna_object@assays$RNA$data
measured = t(measured)

#the plotting function used to visualize the expression patterns
marker_plot = function(gene,cell_umap){
  
  cell_umap$Measured = measured[rownames(cell_umap),gene];
  cell_umap$SuperMap = supermap_imputation[rownames(cell_umap),gene]
  cell_umap$Signac = Signac_imputation[rownames(cell_umap),gene]
  cell_umap$MAESTRO = MAESTRO_imputation[rownames(cell_umap),gene] 
  cell_umap$UnpairReg = UnpairReg_imputation[rownames(cell_umap),gene]
  
  cell_umap$Measured = scale_01(cell_umap$Measured);cell_umap$SuperMap = scale_01(cell_umap$SuperMap)
  cell_umap$Signac = scale_01(cell_umap$Signac);cell_umap$MAESTRO = scale_01(cell_umap$MAESTRO)
  cell_umap$UnpairReg = scale_01(cell_umap$UnpairReg)
  
  p_measured = scatter_plot(method = 'Measured',cell_umap = cell_umap)
  p_supermap = scatter_plot(method = 'SuperMap',cell_umap = cell_umap)
  p_signac = scatter_plot(method = 'Signac',cell_umap = cell_umap)
  p_MAESTRO = scatter_plot(method = 'MAESTRO',cell_umap = cell_umap)
  p_unpairreg = scatter_plot(method = 'UnpairReg',cell_umap = cell_umap)
  
  p_measured+p_supermap+p_signac+p_MAESTRO+p_unpairreg+plot_layout(ncol = 3)+
    patchwork::plot_annotation(title = gene,theme = theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 28, face = "bold", hjust = 0.5)))
}

scale_01 <- function(x) {
  return((x - min(x)) / (max(x) - min(x)))
}

scatter_plot = function(method,cell_umap,legend='none'){
  p = ggplot()+
    geom_point(data=cell_umap,aes_string(x = "wnnUMAP_1", y = "wnnUMAP_2", color = method),size=0.1)+
    scale_color_gradient(low = "grey", high = '#CD2626') +
    theme_bw()+
    #labs(x = "UMAP1", y = "UMAP2")+
    theme(
      panel.grid = element_blank(),
      panel.border = element_rect(color = "black", fill = NA, linewidth = 1), 
      axis.line = element_blank(), 
      axis.ticks = element_blank(), 
      axis.text.x = element_blank(), 
      axis.text.y = element_blank(),
      axis.title.x = element_blank(),
      axis.title.y = element_blank(),
      legend.position = legend,
      legend.text = element_text(size = 13),
      aspect.ratio = 1,
      axis.title = element_text(size = 13),
      plot.caption = element_text(hjust = 0.5)
    )+
    labs(color = "", caption = method) +
    coord_fixed()+
    guides(color = guide_colorbar(barwidth = 1, barheight = 20))
  return(p)
}

cell_umap = as.data.frame(readRDS('cell_umap.RDS'))

marker_plot(gene = 'RBM47',cell_umap = cell_umap)

marker_plot(gene = 'PRF1',cell_umap = cell_umap)

marker_plot(gene = 'LRRK2',cell_umap = cell_umap)

marker_plot(gene = 'CD8B',cell_umap = cell_umap)
